Package: sparseMarkov
Type: Package
Title: Inference in sparse Mixture Transition Distribution (MTD) Markov Chains
Version: 0.1.0
Author: Maiara Gripp
Maintainer: Maiara Gripp <maiaragripp@gmail.com>
Description: Estimates the set os relevant lags from a MTD Markov Chain sample. Can also perfectly simulate a MTD Markov Chain.
